CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper September 23, 1961, pg. 21, reads: "Birthday Celebration - A birthday dinner party was given for little Miss Gina Jenkins, daughter of Mr. and Mrs. James E. Jenkins of 7834 Zinga [Tioga?] St., who was three years old on September 18... - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Two babies, possibly from Jenkins family, seated on bed with chenille bedspread
